"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-07-24-CMG-releases-statement-on-copyright-protection-for-2024-Paris-Olympics-1vv0bmiDorK-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"CGTN  Copied  CMG's 8K ultra-high-definition live broadcast van outside Stade de France in Paris, France.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 310, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 219, \"end\": 222, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"score\": 0.9998536379657099, \"rank\": 0.0001462316485986767, \"text\": \"CMG\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 296, \"end\": 301, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999912961357, \"rank\": 8.703785066242326e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 303, \"end\": 309, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9959441900247784, \"rank\": 0.0022770703640832093, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CMG  China Media Group (CMG) released a statement on Wednesday related to its copyright protection measures for the 2024 Paris Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 311, \"to\": 453, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 317, \"end\": 334, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"China Media Group\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 336, \"end\": 339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"score\": 0.9998536379657099, \"rank\": 0.0001462316485986767, \"text\": \"CMG\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 33rd Summer Olympic Games will take place in Paris, France, from July 26 to August 11.\", \"from\": 455, \"to\": 545, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 464, \"end\": 484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9393548781950151, \"rank\": 0.05105322248318517, \"text\": \"Summer Olympic Games\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 504, \"end\": 509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999912961357, \"rank\": 8.703785066242326e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 511, \"end\": 517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9959441900247784, \"rank\": 0.0022770703640832093, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to an agreement between CMG and the International Olympic Committee, CMG holds exclusive rights for all media and sub-licensing for the Games in the Chinese mainland and Macao Special Administrative Region (MSAR).\", \"from\": 546, \"to\": 769, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 580, \"end\": 583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"score\": 0.9998536379657099, \"rank\": 0.0001462316485986767, \"text\": \"CMG\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 592, \"end\": 623, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 625, \"end\": 628, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"score\": 0.9998536379657099, \"rank\": 0.0001462316485986767, \"text\": \"CMG\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 705, \"end\": 721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mainland_China\", \"score\": 0.9999971628530376, \"rank\": 2.8371550811108086e-06, \"text\": \"Chinese mainland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mainland_China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mainland_China\"}, {\"begin\": 726, \"end\": 731, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Macau\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 5.493760467457654e-13, \"text\": \"Macao\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Macau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Macau\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As of the date CMG released this statement, CMG has authorized Migu, a subsidiary of China Mobile Communications Corporation (CMCC-Migu), to provide coverage of the Games through live broadcasts, delayed broadcasts, video on demand, and short videos.\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 1021, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 786, \"end\": 789, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"score\": 0.9998536379657099, \"rank\": 0.0001462316485986767, \"text\": \"CMG\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 815, \"end\": 818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"score\": 0.9998536379657099, \"rank\": 0.0001462316485986767, \"text\": \"CMG\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 856, \"end\": 868, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Mobile\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3760190220950624e-25, \"text\": \"China Mobile\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Mobile\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Mobile\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Additionally, video platforms Douyin and Kuaishou, as well as internet company Tencent, will offer video on demand and short videos.\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1154, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1052, \"end\": 1058, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Douyin\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}, {\"begin\": 1063, \"end\": 1071, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kuaishou\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kuaishou\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kuaishou\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kuaishou\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Television broadcasts will be available on the Sports Leisure Channel of Beijing Radio and Television Station, the Five-Star Sport News Channel of Shanghai Media Group, and Guangdong TV Sports Channel (excluding new media platforms).\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1388, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1328, \"end\": 1340, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guangdong_Television\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.554069533629275e-19, \"text\": \"Guangdong TV\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guangdong_Television\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guangdong_Television\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"CMG will also collaborate with China Film Group Corporation to offer live viewing services for the Paris Olympics in select theaters nationwide.\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1533, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1389, \"end\": 1392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"score\": 0.9998536379657099, \"rank\": 0.0001462316485986767, \"text\": \"CMG\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 1420, \"end\": 1448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Film_Group_Corporation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"China Film Group Corporation\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Film_Group_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Film_Group_Corporation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Except for the above authorized partners, no organization or individual may use the audio and video content or related broadcast signals of the Games without authorization from CMG.\", \"from\": 1535, \"to\": 1716, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1712, \"end\": 1715, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"score\": 0.9998536379657099, \"rank\": 0.0001462316485986767, \"text\": \"CMG\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This includes, but is not limited to, live broadcasts, delayed broadcasts, on-demand services, carousels, editing, animated images, video downloads, theater screenings, or public place broadcasts.\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1913, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Unauthorized use across various platforms, including television, radio, the Internet, mobile communication networks, IPTV, Internet TV, mobile media TV and application software, as well as accounts and mini-programs on these platforms, is prohibited in the Chinese mainland and MSAR.\", \"from\": 1914, \"to\": 2197, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2171, \"end\": 2187, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mainland_China\", \"score\": 0.9999971628530376, \"rank\": 2.8371550811108086e-06, \"text\": \"Chinese mainland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mainland_China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mainland_China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Additionally, it is prohibited to use CMG's programs for the Games or engage in any form of unfair competition under the guise of live broadcasts, rebroadcasts, or Olympic media cooperation.\", \"from\": 2199, \"to\": 2389, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2237, \"end\": 2240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"score\": 0.9998536379657099, \"rank\": 0.0001462316485986767, \"text\": \"CMG\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This includes, but is not limited to, covert marketing activities exploiting Olympic media rights.\", \"from\": 2390, \"to\": 2488, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"CMG has launched a special copyright protection campaign and will collaborate with various parties to strengthen rights protection efforts.\", \"from\": 2490, \"to\": 2629, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2490, \"end\": 2493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"score\": 0.9998536379657099, \"rank\": 0.0001462316485986767, \"text\": \"CMG\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Effective legal measures will be taken to crack down on infringements of the 2024 Paris Olympic Games program copyright and the use of program resources for unfair competition.\", \"from\": 2630, \"to\": 2806, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The legal responsibilities of relevant entities will be thoroughly investigated and enforced according to the law.\", \"from\": 2807, \"to\": 2921, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 2923, \"to\": 3183, \"entities\": []}]}"